id: pm-cedo0g
title: "GH-664: published daily release fails Bun node:sqlite verification before GitHub Release"
description: "The 2026-07-24 daily pipeline published @unbrained/pm-cli 2026.7.24 and pushed v2026.7.24, then its downstream Release verification failed because Bun 1.3.14 cannot resolve node:sqlite from the bundled CLI. Restore packed Bun compatibility, make post-publish state reporting truthful, recover the missing GitHub Release, and prove automatic release health end to end."
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 1
